API - Application Programming inteface
API - is a method of communication between two systemsCreate - creating data/resource- creating a user- jhon doe - createUser();
Retrieve - retrieve data/resource - existing data or the user we created - jhon doe - getUser();
Update - update the data/resource - updating existing users - jhon doe - updateUser();
Delete - deleting data/resource - existing users- jon doe - deleteUser();Create - POST call
Retrieve - GET call
Update - UPDATE/PUT call
Delete - DELETE callPOST call - creating data
URI - Uniform Resource Identifier
URL - Uniform Resource LocatorURI --> Domain URL/Base URL + service URL/resource
Domain URL/Base URL - http://www.abc.com
service URL/resource - /createUser
URI --> http://www.abc.com/createUser2nd thing we need is - Payload/body
